om convective heat transfer within the fluid, heat generated by fluid friction, and heat exchange with the drill pipe. A vertical temperature distribution is calculated for the drill pipe by accounting for the vertical conduction of heat in the pipe and the convective heat exchange between the pipe and the fluid columns surrounding it. SPEJ P. 23},
