  abstract = {There is an increasing requirement for centralized analysis of drilling data to improve performance. Typically, data from service companies is transmitted from the rig to the clients Real Time Operating Centre (RTOC).  A major problem is the quality of this data, which can lead to incorrect analysis and a breakdown in trust between the rig and the RTOC. Currently real time data is, at best, only checked for completeness.

